<p>The staff profile pattern includes a title, name, short biography, contact details, optional photo and optional call to action.</p>

<ul>
	<li>The <code>bio</code> should be no more than 140 characters.</li>
	<li>Image must be <code>200px</code> square.</li>
	<li>If using a call-to-action, an image must be present as well.</li>
	<li>When the call to action is present, then the <code>title</code> links to the call to action URL too.</li>
	<li>"Email", "Phone" and "Fax" should always be present if available for the person. However, additional fields may be used: "Website", "Twitter"</li>	
</ul>

